		<RichText x="739" y="255" width="436" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">萨满施法，在玩家处连续生成至多3次的突震，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">60%</span><span>伤害。<br/>「怒面」状态下，每次突震将产生额外的冲击波，造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">70%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="511" width="436" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">萨满将随机召唤6枚日落果或卷心菜，均造成<span color="#b8b8b8">100%</span><span>伤害。<br/>「怒面」状态下不施放。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/丘尔德里克.assets/Image_14.png')" x="719" y="169">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/丘尔德里克.assets/Image_15.png')" x="720" y="426">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/丘尔德里克.assets/Image_16.png')" x="720" y="681">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/丘尔德里克.assets/Image_17.png')" x="718" y="905">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="767" width="408" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离玩家较近时，萨满挥杖击飞玩家，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">80%</span><span>伤害。<br/>「怒面」状态下，挥杖范围变大。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="991" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">萨满立即翘杆进行3次下落攻击，每次造成<span color="#b8b8b8">70%</span><span>伤害；返回中心时只下落一次。<br/>「怒面」状态下，每次下落将产生额外2道冲击波，均造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="898" y="59" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#96673d" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#96673d">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="575" y="116" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="30" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="504" height="34" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.5019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="30" color="#ffffff">元素能量：WP[75,50,25,0x3],WO[0]</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#ffdfbf" distance="16" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1284" width="443" height="250" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">烹饪进度：满进度100，汤锅为点燃状态时，前20%进度每0.5秒+2.5，后续每0.5秒+7.5。<br/>美味汤锅：<span color="#ffe599">30岩</span><span>盾，会记录伤害但无伤害转化，同时伤害会转移伤害到大萨满身上，持续16s；破坏后萨满瘫痪。<br/>用</span><span color="#ffdfbf">1</span><span>次</span><span color="#ffbfbf">火元素</span><span>攻击可点燃汤锅，用</span><span color="#ffdfbf">2</span><span>次</span><span color="#99ffff">冰</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffe599">岩</span><span>/</span><span color="#7fffd7">风</span><span>攻击，或者</span><span color="#ffdfbf">1</span><span>次</span><span color="#ffacff">雷</span><span>/</span><span color="#7fbfff">水</span><span>攻击会熄灭锅，</span><span color="#99ff85">草元素</span><span>攻击无用。锅的「火」为特效，仅指示状态，不是真火。<br/><br/>汤成：</span><span color="#ffdfbf">恢复20%生命值</span><span>，全抗</span><span color="#ffdfbf">提升110%</span><span>(</span><span color="#ffdfbf">深渊290%</span><span>)，持续30s。<br/>炊生：攻击</span><span color="#ffdfbf">提升100%</span><span>，持续30s。<br/>破釜：破坏后，造成</span><span color="#ffdfbf">(锅所受伤害+10%生命值)</span><span>的真伤，不超过20%生命值，同时</span><span color="#ffdfbf">全抗降至-50%</span><span>，瘫痪10s。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
