		<RichText x="738" y="1247" width="442" height="287" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">萨满架设「<span textDecoration="underline">美味汤锅</span><span>」并进行烹饪，烹饪时长16s，期间周围将不间断产生流溢余火，对范围内目标造成</span><span color="#ff9999">70%</span><span>伤害。根据</span><span textDecoration="underline">烹饪进度</span><span>可产生不同效果：<br/>烹饪进度完成为</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#bfffbf">汤成</span><span>：进入绿色「满足」状态，抗性提升，持续30s；<br/>烹饪进度未满为</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#ffb299">炊生</span><span>：进入红色「怒面」状态，攻击力翻倍，持续30s；<br/>成功破坏汤锅则</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#ffffbf">破釜</span><span>：根据期间汤锅所受伤害返还真伤，抗性降低，瘫痪10s。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/丘尔德里克.assets/Image_31.png')" x="719" y="1162">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/丘尔德里克.assets/Image_32.png')" x="576" y="1174" blendMode="normal">
